@SnapThought.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5287

### Capture a thought (raw content + optional tags) -> reformat -> store
# @name capture
POST {{SnapThought.Api_HostAddress}}/api/snapthoughts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "ok so the idea is basically capture a thought fast like a snap, tag it, and the machine cleans it up later",
  "tags": ["idea", "product"]
}

### Retrieve the thought just captured (uses the id from the response above)
GET {{SnapThought.Api_HostAddress}}/api/snapthoughts/{{capture.response.body.id}}
Accept: application/json

### List all stored thoughts (newest first)
GET {{SnapThought.Api_HostAddress}}/api/snapthoughts
Accept: application/json

###
